                <td bgcolor="#ECECEC" valign="top" width="100" nowrap><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2"><b>Jeddia</b></font></td>
                <td bgcolor="#ECECEC" valign="top" width="100%"><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2"><small>Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;09/20/2003&nbsp;: 9:53:58 PM</small><hr size="2"><span class="spnMessageText"> So let's hear your stories of the complete idiots you've had to group with for the past 2 weeks.  As necros, we all know what it's like to either a) be used to solo'ing, or b) only grouping with guildies.  Now with LDoN we find ourselves enduring the pick-up groups to speed up the point farming...<br /><br />So far my main complaints have been with the chanters, gawd they suck.  90% of the time, I just take over the crowd control.  They wanna Tash the mob, then leisurely hit their "TASHED" hotkey, then slow it when the mob's at like 20% health.  I think inexperienced enchanters should be thrust into more difficult crowd control scenarios before they are allowed near LDoN.  Necro's use mezz and slow like total pro's only because most likely when we learned how to do it - we were solo'ing and it meant dying if we didn't get it right.<br /><br />I grouped with a 65 paladin who not only *hotkeyed* his request for a twitch, but started freaking out abd called me a hacker when I rezzed his sorry ass.<br /><br />A cleric who just pulled random mobs while we had a camp full already and started melee'ing them with his fucking summoned hammer.  They shoulda never gave those hammers to clerics lol.<br /><br />A shaman who, and I shit you not - this is true...  He did nothing the entire mission but casts Tnarg's on me (when I didn't need it) and ninja loot every mob we killed.  He never said a word, he didn't slow, he didn't summon a pet, he didn't buff.  /sigh<br /><br />And my personal favorite so far...  The group that actually ejected (targeted me and disbanded me) me from the group so they could replace me with a level 59 enchanter....  I found them naked outside the crypt entrance 30 minutes later when I was going in with a group of 4 necros.<br /><br />Anyone else?<br /><br /><br /><br /></span></font></td>
